lass=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nSubject <br />\nPlease ensure the safety of our staff on 5th August Strike<br />\n<br />\nContent <br />\nDear Management of ___________,  <br />\n<br />\nAccording to sources as diverse as newspaper headlines (see attached link below) and various discussions on Facebook and web forums, a major strike is expected on 5th August (next Monday), with large scale assembly is also expected in our area. I am worried for both public safety and public transportation logistics for the day. <br />\n<br />\nAccording to OCCUPATIONAL SAFETY AND HEALTH ORDINANCE, CHAPTER 509, Employers should contribute to safety and health in their workplaces by: <br />\n* providing and maintaining safe access to and egress from the workplaces; and <br />\n* providing and maintaining a safe and healthy work environment <br />\n<br />\nMay I seek a clarification on management&rsquo;s plan?<br />\n<br />\nWill there be any disciplinary action if the employee decided to join the strike on 5 August 2019?<br />\n<br />\nNews- HK protesters call for citywide strike on August 5<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.asiatimes.com/2019/07/article/hk-protesters-call-for-citywide-strike-on-august-5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.asiatimes.com%2F2019%2F07%2Farticle%2Fhk-protesters-call-for-citywide-strike-on-august-5&d=7fFLqiM2ByXH61viL1oyjFuXAffr%2FfAYLX%2F1af%2FGhNY%3D&h=a1854265\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.asiatimes.com/2019/07/article/hk-protesters-call-for-citywide-strike-on-august-5</a>"},{"pid":"1fa8d529f7a67a2ef08d69e73f2b3d6070e67eb5","tid":1396222,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T05:21:04.000Z","msg":"老流認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62e754539c720acabb2a6f68711ed6315e971421","tid":1396222,"uid":215505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T05:23:29.000Z","msg":"老唯認同"},{"pid":"d9fc7a703df8287b0e2843900fd23e